Quickstrike:




"Ya can go on yer way," Quickstrike said to Mantella without turning his 
head to her. "But come 'round if ah call fer ya." He walked away to explore 
the hallways in the ship. He wondered how he could press his luck. He 
wondered about doing back to the confinement area where Rattrap was.
